Thanks for using Bamazon! 

Instructions:

Bamazon allows you to order the latest videogame consoles! Upon running the program, it will list what's available, pricing, and the item's unique Id code. Pay special attention to the Id code as it is what Bamazon uses to handle your order.

Answer two simple prompts and it will take care of the rest! For example: "Ninsw-03" and "1" will tell the system that you wish to order one Nintendo Switch. Enjoy using Bamazon!
